<h2>Delivery</h2>

<p>
Deliveries will be made every Tuesday between 9am and 12pm.  At this time, we can only deliver to Richmond and Vancouver.  It is your responsibility to refrigerate your meals upon delivery or leave a cooler with ice packs in it at the delivery spot you indicate.   All food is designed to stay fresh in the refrigerator for at least 3 days.  Many of the meals freeze well and are marked to indicate this, so if you don't eat them within the 3 days, you can pop them in the freezer and eat them later.  Please reheat the food to a temperature of 74C (165F) before eating.  All food will be delivered in recyclable or compostable containers. 
</p>


<h2>The Paleo Diet</h2>

<p>
A paleo diet excludes grains, dairy, legumes, refined sweeteners, high omega-6 vegetable oils and other processed foods.   Plenty of vegetables, fruits, meat, fish, seeds and nuts are eaten instead.  This diet would be suitable for many elimination diets and my hope is that people will use this opportunity to help them explore their own food intolerances or simply to incorporate more nutrient-dense foods in their diet to see how it makes them feel.  These meals will be lower in carbohydrates and higher in saturated fat than what many people are used to eating, but I believe this is actually a much healthier way to eat.</p>

<p>For more info, check out this video by a respected health care practitioner in the paleo community encouraging people to try the paleo diet:</p>
